data.description: Great Opportunity at a 'Great Value' on this Charming Turn of the Century 2 Story Cinder Block Home on 40 or 80 Acres!!! Property has a Casita Style Apartment/Workshop, 24x12 Loaf Shed/Barn, 20x14 1 Car Garage & 16x10 Storage Shed *Very Unique Home w/ 4 Bedrooms on Upper Level with Hardwood Floors to Include Master Bedroom Walking Out to 20x10 Deck. Main Level Boasts Large Living Room, Family/Dining Room w/Beamed Ceilings & Woodburning Stove, Spacious Kitchen, Both Walking out to 28x13 Enclosed Sunroom/Laundry Room *Mature Trees & Fully Fenced Property!!! Perfect Home for a Handyman or a Larger Family to Have All the Animals & Live Peacefully in the Country! 10 Minutes to Calhan!! **Home was Originally the Infamous "Bean Farm"!!
